ableToRepay(address).details: check if borrow amount is exceed than collateral

borrowInterestOfUser(address,address).details: calculate borrow interest of user depends on his creditScore, collateral ratio and supply of borrowed asset

returns._0: max borrow percentage of user - max: maxBorrow, min: 0

increaseCollateral(uint256).details: increase collateral amount from user's eth supply

params.amount: - amount of supply to convert to collateral

maxBorrowOfUser(address).details: calculate max borrow of user depends on his creditScore

returns._0: max borrow percentage of user - max: maxBorrow, min: 0

supply(address,uint256).details: lenders deposit `amount` of `token`   transfer token from msg.sender and give wrapped token(similiar with cToken)

totalRepayAmount(address).details: get total repay amount of user in eth

valueInEth(address,uint256).details: Calculate eth value for `amount` of `token` (using price oracle)

withdrawSupply(address,uint256).details: lenders withdraw `amount` of `token`   transfer token from msg.sender and give wrapped token(similiar with cToken) requirements - cannot withdraw eth if remaining balance is lower than collateral
